reviewText: Some reviewers complain about the video and it's sounds and special effects. Ok so the videographer should find a new job. Use FF on your remote, get to the part you paid for and glean knowledge from a journeyman.

All of these DVDs are well produced with multiple camera angles and dramatic music. Paul, as always is not only a master woodworker he is a great teacher. The Artisan Media DVDs are amazing! I want all of them.
